1 AN ACT concerning
2 Public School Construction and Renovation – Solar Canopies for School
3 Parking Lots – Underground Infrastructure
4 School Buildings – Solar Technologies – Parking Lot Solar Canopies
5 FOR the purpose of requiring that certain construction projects or major renovation
6 projects of public school buildings be designed, engineered, and constructed in a
7 manner so that school parking lots are equipped with the appropriate underground
8 infrastructure necessary to support solar canopy installation; and generally relating
9 to public school construction and renovations including parking lot solar canopies in
10 the evaluation of the use of solar technologies required for the construction or major
11 renovation of school buildings; and generally relating to school buildings and solar
12 technology.
